title: Fetch and Wayne Reaves Dealer Software & Websites to offer an integrated auto insurance solution for car buying customers
text:
Fetch!
VIRGINIA BEACH, Va. and MACON, Ga. , Oct. 21, FetchaQuote: .com (Fetch) is pleased to announce the integration of its electronic auto insurance service into the Wayne Reaves Dealer Management Software. Wayne Reaves has been delivering dealer management software to automobile dealerships since 1987. Fetch's integration with Wayne Reaves will allow a car-buying customer to obtain multiple insurance Quote: s within seconds and purchase a policy online while at the dealership. By working with Fetch, Wayne Reaves expands its portfolio of outstanding service providers to include an integrated automobile insurance solution.
Joseph Kindley , President of Fetch stated, "Wayne Reaves has been helping dealerships with software needs since 1987, and Fetch is excited to be on the Wayne Reaves platform. With this integration, Wayne Reaves' dealers will have an integrated option to allow their customers to shop for and purchase affordable automobile insurance from nationally recognized insurance carriers.
Wayne Reaves is happy to be able to provide the Fetch insurance solution to dealers using its online DMS. We have worked with Fetch to provide a smooth integration that saves valuable time by transmitting the customer's information with the click of a button. It is our belief that the ability to help a customer leave a dealership with insurance in place with competitive Quote: s from multiple companies will benefit the customer as well as the dealership.
About Wayne Reaves
Wayne Reaves is a leading provider of dealer management software, customizable responsive dealer websites, mobile dealer solutions and web-based title pawn and repair shop software. As the most trusted name in the digital space, dealers rely on Wayne Reaves solutions to sell more cars, save time and increase productivity. No other digital partner provides dealers with the depth and breadth of experience in the dealer industry. Learn more at WayneReaves.com
About Fetch!
FetchaQuote: .com is a patent-pending insurance solution for car-buying customers. Fetch sends a customer's information to multiple insurance carriers at once, returns all the Quote: s side-by-side on a single internet page, and gives the customer the ability to click-through to purchase insurance directly from the insurance carrier's website. Not only does Fetch help uninsured customers buy insurance quickly, but Fetch also helps customers with insurance to quickly shop their auto insurance among nationally-recognized carriers. For more information about Fetch, contact Frederick Rector at fred@fetchaQuote: .com or call 757-739-0230. www.fetchaQuote: .com
